<P>Prie&s;ts, Officers, Soldiers, and other Attendants.</P>
<P>SCENE <HI>in</HI> Kent, <HI>about Twenty Years after the fir&s;t Inva&s;ion of</HI> Britain <HI>by the</HI> Saxons.</P>
